{"id": 3055, "genre": 1000, "title": "如果可以的话，你最希望把生活中的哪些事交给“代服务”？", "description": "虽然自己都能做到，但偶尔还是会觉得，把它们外包给别人代劳似乎也挺不错。（题图来自：iStock ©️ miakievy）", "record_count": 3308, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191110235110ftR1vhBpPFVyIJaS.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-10T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6032, "title": "如果可以的话，你最希望把生活中的哪些事交给“代服务”？", "content": "如果可以的话，你最希望把生活中的哪些事交给“代服务”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349244, "content": "代唠嗑，把尬聊/彩虹屁这些事儿都交给专业人士", "image": "img/option/option/20191110230622pPWX163sd74jAQaC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349245, "content": "代吃零食，自己吃怕胖，看别人吃过个眼瘾就行", "image": "img/option/option/201911102308491EPT03KWzrwtgvQu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349246, "content": "代收纳，把扔哪个留哪个的断舍离烦恼交给别人", "image": "img/option/option/20191110231111Xje7YDHhBKokNtSx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349247, "content": "代等位，替自己去人超多的网红奶茶店/餐厅排队", "image": "img/option/option/20191110231454BJZPeQT2MOGc5pVz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349249, "content": "代养猫/遛狗，自己没空可以交给别人照顾一阵子", "image": "img/option/option/20191110233652MLYZKx9Qu6mhj4EB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349250, "content": "代跑腿，请别人帮自己下楼买东西/取快递/扔垃圾", "image": "img/option/option/20191110232309fciy4hbL8Iu60mz5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349251, "content": "代叫醒，对自己的闹钟免疫了，请别人帮忙叫起床", "image": "img/option/option/20191110233251vEPmbU7L6s8othiY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349252, "content": "代上班/代通勤，留一点工资给自己当生活费就行", "image": "img/option/option/20191110233643dA2FeC4TwaBpD1X7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349253, "content": "都不需要/我有别的需求", "image": "img/option/option/201911102336328kLSAc3Op1H9EIjh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}